description: WeSC AB engages in the design, marketing, and sale of clothes and accessories. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 30 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2008-05-19. The firm acquires and develops specialist companies with exposure to construction and infrastructure contracts. The firm actively looking for companies with proved business models, market positions and predictable cash flows where it has the potential to be involved and contribute to continued positive development.
